OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FA man on trial for killing a first-
OL,7,Fyear university student has denied a
OL,8,Fcharge of manslaughter.
OL,10,FVickrum Digwa is accused at
OL,11,FSouthampton Crown Court of the murder
OL,12,Fof 18-year-old Henry Nowak, from
OL,13,FChafford Hundred, Essex, in Belmont
OL,14,FRoad, Southampton, on December 3 2025.
OL,16,FThe 23-year-old is also charged with
OL,17,Fcarrying a knife in public and his
OL,18,Fmother, Kiran Kaur, 53, is accused of
OL,19,Fassisting an offender by removing a
OL,20,Fweapon from the scene.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
