PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779538270
OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FThe court has heard that Digwa was
OL,7,Fcarrying a kirpan ` a religious knife
OL,8,F` with a 21cm blade which the
OL,9,Fprosecution says caused five stab
OL,10,Fwounds to Mr Nowak, including two to
OL,11,Fthe back of his legs and a fatal wound
OL,12,Fto the chest.
OL,14,FThe judge, William Mousley KC, told
OL,15,Fthe jury that he had ordered Digwa to
OL,16,Fface a charge of manslaughter as an
OL,17,Falternative to the murder charge.
OL,19,FThe defendant then pleaded not guilty
OL,20,Fto the offence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
