PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779538270
OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FThe jury has seen footage showing
OL,7,FHenry Nowak at the Hobbit pub in
OL,8,FBevois Valley before the incident.
OL,10,FExplaining the new charge, the judge
OL,11,Ftold the jurors: "If a person may not
OL,12,Fhave deliberately have caused the
OL,13,Ffatal injury or may not have intended
OL,14,Fto kill or cause reasonably serious
OL,15,Fharm, he or she is not guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder.
OL,26,@sD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
