PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779538270
OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,F"Then there is an alternative charge
OL,7,Fand that charge is the offence of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and a person commits the
OL,9,Foffence of manslaughter if he or she
OL,10,Fdeliberately, unlawfully and not in
OL,11,Freasonable self defence caused the
OL,12,Fdeath of another by an act that a
OL,13,Freasonable person would realise could
OL,14,Fresult in some, if not really serious,
OL,15,Fharm."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
