OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FResponding to a question by the jury
OL,7,Fas to whether it was illegal to carry
OL,8,Fa knife of the size of the kirpan
OL,9,Fcarried by the defendant, the judge
OL,10,Fsaid it would have to be for a good
OL,11,Freason such as "only for self defence"
OL,12,For for religious reasons.
OL,14,FThe jury has seen footage from various
OL,15,Fcctv cameras of Henry Novak at various
OL,16,Fstages that evening when he was on a
OL,17,Fnight out
OL,26,@sD@POUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
