PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779538270
OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FHe added: "It is for Vickrum Digwa to
OL,7,Fprove that it is more likely than not
OL,8,Fthat he had a good reason for having
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,FGiving legal directions to the jury,
OL,12,Fthe judge added: "Do not allow any
OL,13,Ffeelings of sympathy, your decision
OL,14,Fmust be unbiased."
OL,16,FGiving evidence, the defendant told
OL,17,Fthe court that Mr Nowak, who he
OL,18,Fdescribed as drunk, had racially
OL,19,Fabused him before punching him and
OL,20,Fknocking his turban off.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@DO]tD@ROUvD@RO]
