CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779538270
OL,3,CMan on trial for killing student
OL,4,Cpleads not guilty to manslaughter
OL,6,FHe said that he had stabbed Mr Nowak
OL,7,Fto the back of his legs in self
OL,8,Fdefence after Mr Nowak had threatened
OL,9,Fhim and grabbed him by the hair, but
OL,10,Fsaid he had not realised at the time
OL,11,Fhe had caused the fatal stab wound to
OL,12,Fhis chest.
OL,14,FThe defendants deny the charges and
OL,15,Fthe trial continues.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
